  <CalDefinition Description="Enable use of learning algorithm which looks at expected Propulsion Power and actual Propulsion Power and creates a multiplier for Low, Med, and High Power.   This will use a multiplier in future MyMode events for RoadLoad compensation." Name="KeMMMR_b_UseRdLdLrng" References="GIS674" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
