      <Description>With agreement from Shanmukh Rajurs and Terry Meehan, updated the allowable minimum value defined for the KnMMMR_v_RdLdSpeed float array calibration from a minumum value of 1.4E-45 to 0. Note, made this update as a result of the needed use case of another float array calibration (KtMMMR_t_HVACSwtchMntn )within this caldef file having a default value of zero, also updated the minimum value of this float array calibration (KnMMMR_v_RdLdSpeed) to also allow the flexibltiy to set one of the array parameters for this calibration to zero in the future via a CAL override if it were to ever be needed too.</Description>
