      <Description>With agreement from Shanmukh Rajurs and Terry Meehan, updated the minimum value defined for the KtMMMR_t_HVACSwtchMntn float array calibration from a minumum value of 1.4E-45 to 0. Note, this update had to made to correct an issue with the default value for one of the array parameters (KtMMMR_t_HVACSwtchMntn[2]=0.0 ) needed being below the predefined allowable/workable minimum value.</Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
